OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSt Kitts is 'not totally   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffree' under the King - PM  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Prime Minister of a Caribbean      
OL,6, nation has told the BBC his country is 
OL,7, "not totally free" as long as King     
OL,8, Charles III remains head of state.     
OL,10,FDr Terrance Drew said that a public    
OL,11,Fconsultation on whether St Kitts and   
OL,12,FNevis should become a republic would   
OL,13,Fbegin during his leadership.           
OL,15,FHe also said he would welcome an       
OL,16,Fapology from the monarchy for its      
OL,17,Fhistoric links to the slave trade.     
OL,19,FBuckingham Palace told the BBC the King
OL,20,Ftakes slavery "profoundly seriously".  
